🇷🇸#Serbia to produce Chinese vaccine locally.
Serbian President Aleksandar Vucic @avucic on Thursday said the country will start producing 🇨🇳#China's #Sinopharm #COVID19 #vaccine by October 15, after a meeting with 🇦🇪#UAE Crown Prince Mohammed bin Zayed Al Nahyan in Abu Dhabi. https://t.co/5XuzkWNZGA
